title: Mera Haque
subTitle: A young hooligan who looks exactly like a murdered prince is taken to the palace and made to impersonate him. Schemes, however, go sideways as the young man seems to have plans of his own.

title: Keemat
subTitle: Sudha goes undercover on Gopal's instructions to put an end to a human trafficking business that abducts young women. But they are unaware that the assignment is compromised and poses a grave risk.

title: Chandan Ka Palna
subTitle: Ajit's perfect marriage to Shobha turns upside down after she starts behaving strangely with him and his mother, leading to a disturbed life.

title: Tumhare Liye
subTitle: Gauri and Prakash visit a temple in Jodhpur during their honeymoon after which, she starts to act strange. But, the couple is unaware that it is due to a truth hidden in their past lives.

title: Baadshah
subTitle: An amateur detective, Raj, goes by the nickname of Baadshah. But this name soon causes a misunderstanding that lands him in the middle of a conspiracy to assassinate the chief minister of Goa.

title: Banarasi Babu
subTitle: Sohan Lal, a rich businessman, is abducted and imprisoned. When Gulabiya helps him to escape from the prison, he meets with an accident. He then attempts to sort out his jeopardised life.

title: Pataal Bhairavi
subTitle: Ramu, a poor man, falls for a princess, but her father forbids the relation due to Ramu's poverty. Later, things take a turn for the worse when Ramu becomes rich, but it endangers his paramour.

title: Ek Hi Bhool
subTitle: Ram's affair with Sadhana's close friend leads to their painful separation and a shattered marriage. Years later, their son Raju attempts to reunite them.

title: Teri Meherbaniyan
subTitle: Ram, an honest man, falls in love with a woman named Bijli and goes on to help the people of her village. However, the region's corrupt leader, Thakur Vijay Singh, soon begins to plot against him.

title: Dacait
subTitle: After being mercilessly beaten and abandoned to die, a young man is rescued by a band of dacoits, who nurse him back to health in their hidden lair.

title: Razia Sultan
subTitle: Razia Sultan, the first female ruler of the Delhi Sultanate, lands in trouble and loses her kingdom when she falls in love with Jamal-ud-Din Yakut, an Abyssinian slave.

title: Anita
subTitle: When Anita commits suicide, Neeraj suspects foul play and decides to investigate the truth. However, things take a turn when he starts seeing Anita everywhere.

title: Chalti Ka Naam Gaadi
subTitle: Brijmohan, a mechanic, swears off women after a bad experience. However, when a headstrong woman arrives at his garage, he is forced to reconsider his opinion.

title: Bhuvan Shome
subTitle: A lonely bureaucrat goes on holiday to a village in Gujarat where a young peasant woman helps him see beyond his job and develop a newfound empathy for people.

title: Woh 7 Din
subTitle: Anand, a doctor, realises that Maya, his wife, loves someone else but married him out of coercion. Thus, he sets out to reunite the lovers, but they don't want to be together anymore.

title: Kalicharan
subTitle: When Prabhakar, an honest cop, is murdered by Din Dayal, a powerful crime lord, Khanna recruits his doppelganger Kalicharan to defeat Din Dayal.

title: Pukar
subTitle: Major Jaidev saves a politician from the clutches of a dreaded terrorist. However, the terrorist joins hands with his childhood friend Anjali to ruin his life.

title: Bobby
subTitle: Raja, the son of a rich Hindu businessman, falls in love with Bobby, a poor Catholic girl. Though their families try to keep them away from each other, they strive to be together.

title: Kuchhe Dhaage
subTitle: To avenge his father's death, Lakhan kills Roopa's father, Tulsiram, in cold blood. Enraged, Roopa decides to kill him, but fate has its own plans.

title: Saagar
subTitle: Raja secretly loves Mona, but she is in love with Ravi. However, Ravi's grandmother disapproves of their relationship and asks Mona to forget him and marry someone else.

title: Aap To Aise Na The
subTitle: Vijay, who owns a furniture store, is in love with Varsha. However, Vijay's life takes a drastic turn when she decides to marry his friend Vikram, a rich man, who promises her a better life.

title: Narsingh Avatar
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Chameli Ki Shaadi
subTitle: Charandas and Chameli develop feelings for each other. However, caste differences lead their families to oppose their budding relationship.

title: Waris
subTitle: Frustrated by the king's behaviour, the queen leaves the kingdom with her son. Years later, when the king dies, the palace officials search for his son to claim the throne.

title: Humjoli
subTitle: Gopaldas, a villager, dreams of becoming rich and, thus, marries Roopa, an heiress. However, his greed knows no bounds when he plots Roopa's murder to inherit her property.

title: Aman
subTitle: Dr Gautamdas, a well-educated man from London, moves to Japan during the aftermath of the Hiroshima and Nagasaki bombing, where he falls in love with Meloda.

title: Dacait
subTitle: After being mercilessly beaten and abandoned to die, a young man is rescued by a band of dacoits, who nurse him back to health in their hidden lair.

title: Karz
subTitle: Monty discovers the shocking truth about his past life when he was killed by his gold-digger wife, while his family was rendered homeless. Supported by his lover, he decides to set things right.
